## Ownership Boundaries
- `common` app: end-user identity, OTP, profile/account primitives.
- `partners` app: partner auth/profile, package operations, partner wallet and website package listing endpoints.
- `booking` app: booking lifecycle, partner-side booking actions, complaints/reviews/requests, plus v1 booking endpoints.
- `management` app: super-admin approvals, transfers, KPI/report endpoints, hotel master catalog.
- `chat` app: user/partner inbox/message APIs and websocket routing.
- FE API ownership:
  - Web: `src/api/AuthApi.js`, `src/api/apiService.js`, `src/api/homepageApi.js`, `src/api/listingApi.js`, `src/api/packageDetailApi.js`
  - Admin: `src/utility/AuthApis.js`, `src/utility/Api.js`, `src/utility/Super-Admin-Api.js`
  - Operator: `src/api/authAPI.js`, `src/api/companyAPI.js`, `src/api/PackageAPI.js`, `src/api/BookingApi.js`, `src/api/DashboardApi.js`, `src/api/WalletApi.js`, `src/api/ReviewRatingAPI.js`, `src/api/complaintsAPI.js`

